statement.title: Problem Description
statement.content: Given a sequence, you're asked whether there exists a consecutive subsequence whose sum is divisible by m.  output YES, otherwise output NO

statement.title: Input
statement.content:
The first line of the input has an integer T ($1 \leq T \leq 10$), which represents the number of test cases.
For each test case, there are two lines:
1.The first line contains two positive integers n, m ($1 \leq n \leq 100000$, $1 \leq m \leq 5000$).
2.The second line contains n positive integers x ($1 \leq x \leq 100$) according to the sequence.

statement.title: Output
statement.content: Output T lines, each line print a YES or NO.
